# Veliora.AI — Canonical Architectural Documentation (Part 3)

## Familia Realtime Communication, Database Schema & System Inventory

> **Document Scope:** Part 3 of 3. Covers the Familia real-time communication platform (Architecture B), the complete database schema for both architectures, supporting services, and system inventory.

---

## 14. Familia — Real-Time Communication Platform

**Directory:** [realtime_communication/](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./realtime_communication)

A self-contained FastAPI sub-application mounted at `/api/v1` on the main app. Implements a cross-cultural human connection platform.

### 14.1 Architecture

```
realtime_communication/
├── config.py              # Pydantic settings (Supabase, Deepgram, Cartesia, Gemini, Google Translate)
├── models/
│   └── schemas.py         # 30+ Pydantic request/response models
├── routers/               # 20 API routers
│   ├── auth.py            # Signup, login, JWT verification
│   ├── profiles.py        # Profile CRUD, avatar, languages, status
│   ├── matching.py        # Role-based matching, smart matching algorithm
│   ├── friends.py         # Search, friend requests, accept/reject, unfriend
│   ├── chat.py            # Messages, media upload, polls, reactions, WebSocket
│   ├── contests.py        # Bonding contests with synchronized questions
│   ├── games.py           # Game catalog, sessions, scoring
│   ├── live_games.py      # Real-time multiplayer games
│   ├── _live_games_new.py # Updated live games (iterative)
│   ├── family_rooms.py    # Room CRUD, membership, potluck events, room chat
│   ├── presence.py        # Online/offline status, last_active tracking
│   ├── privacy.py         # Privacy settings management
│   ├── safety.py          # Reporting, blocking, moderation queue
│   ├── verification.py    # Video/voice/photo identity verification
│   ├── translation.py     # On-demand translation endpoints
│   ├── voice.py           # STT/TTS for voice messages
│   ├── calls.py           # Audio/video call logging
│   ├── questions.py       # Personal Q&A system for contests
│   └── xp.py              # XP dashboard, gifting, leaderboards
├── services/
│   ├── auth_service.py        # JWT extraction (get_current_user_id)
│   ├── supabase_client.py     # Supabase connection (service role)
│   ├── translation_service.py # Google Translate + Gemini cultural context
│   ├── matching_service.py    # Smart matching algorithm
│   ├── xp_service.py          # XP award/gift/level-up engine
│   ├── notification_service.py# Push notification dispatch
│   ├── background_tasks.py    # Streak tracking, XP decay
│   ├── contest_service.py     # Contest question generation
│   ├── deepgram_stt.py        # Speech-to-text wrapper
│   └── cartesia_tts.py        # Text-to-speech wrapper
└── database.txt               # Complete SQL schema (716 lines)
```

