### 14.4 WebSocket Chat — `routers/chat.py` (849 lines)

**File:** [chat.py](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./realtime_communication/routers/chat.py)

**ConnectionManager** — Singleton managing WebSocket connections:
```python
class ConnectionManager:
    active_connections: Dict[str, Set[WebSocket]]  # relationship_id → set of connections
    
    async def connect(ws, relationship_id)     # Accept + register
    def disconnect(ws, relationship_id)         # Remove from set
    async def broadcast(relationship_id, msg, exclude=None)  # Fan-out to all peers
```

**WebSocket Endpoint:** `WS /api/v1/chat/ws/{relationship_id}/{user_id}`

Supported message types:
| Type | Action |
|------|--------|
| `typing` | Broadcast typing indicator to partner |
| `stopped_typing` | Clear typing indicator |
| `read_receipt` | Mark all unread messages as read, broadcast receipt |
| `message` | Full message send with translation, fact extraction, XP award |

**REST Endpoints:**

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/chat/send` | POST | Send message with auto-translation and fact extraction |
| `/chat/upload-media` | POST | Upload image/video/voice → Supabase Storage → send as message |
| `/chat/messages/{relationship_id}` | GET | Paginated message history (marks as read) |
| `/chat/relationship/{relationship_id}` | GET | Full relationship details with feature unlock status |
| `/chat/poll/create` | POST | WhatsApp-style polls with voting |
| `/chat/poll/{poll_id}/vote` | POST | Vote on poll option |
| `/chat/poll/{poll_id}` | GET | Fetch poll with all votes and results |
| `/chat/message/{message_id}/react` | POST | Toggle emoji reactions |
| `/chat/message/{message_id}` | DELETE | Soft-delete (sender only) |
| `/chat/message/{message_id}/forward` | POST | Forward to another relationship |
| `/chat/gift-xp` | POST | Gift XP to partner (creates system message) |

