### 14.4 XP & Relationship Levels — `services/xp_service.py` (295 lines)

**File:** [xp_service.py](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./realtime_communication/services/xp_service.py)

**10-Level Relationship Progression:**

| Level | Name | Bond Points | Unlocked Feature |
|-------|------|-------------|-----------------|
| 1 | Stranger | 0 | Text messaging |
| 2 | Acquaintance | 50 | Emojis & reactions |
| 3 | Bonded | 150 | Audio calls |
| 4 | Close | 300 | Video calls |
| 5 | Family | 500 | Global Family Room |
| 6 | Trusted | 750 | Custom themes |
| 7 | Kindred | 1000 | Priority matching |
| 8 | Soulbound | 1500 | Mentor badge |
| 9 | Eternal | 2000 | Cultural Ambassador |
| 10 | Legendary | 3000 | Digital Family Book |

**`calculate_level(bond_points)`** — Linear threshold lookup (different from AI persona's sqrt curve).

**`award_xp(user_id, amount, source)`:**
1. Ensure `realtime_xp_realtime` row exists (upsert)
2. Increment `current_xp` and `total_xp_earned`
3. Log to `xp_transactions_realtime` with full metadata
4. Send notification

**`gift_xp(sender_id, receiver_id, amount)`:**
1. Verify sender has sufficient balance
2. Deduct from sender, log `gifted_out` transaction
3. Add to receiver, log `gifted_in` transaction
4. Notify receiver

**`check_and_level_up(relationship_id)`:**
1. Fetch current bond_points and level
2. Calculate new level from thresholds
3. If level increased: update relationship, create milestone, notify both users

### 14.5 Friends System — `routers/friends.py` (476 lines)

**File:** [friends.py](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./realtime_communication/routers/friends.py)

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/friends/search` | GET | Search profiles by `?query=` (matches username/display_name), excludes banned |
| `/friends/request/{target_id}` | POST | Send friend request — checks: not self, not banned, no existing pending, privacy |
| `/friends/respond/{request_id}` | POST | Accept/reject request. Accept creates `relationships_realtime` row + notifies |
| `/friends/requests` | GET | List incoming/outgoing pending requests with sender/receiver profiles |
| `/friends/list` | GET | All active bonds with enriched partner data (display_name, avatar, country, care_score) |
| `/friends/{friend_id}/profile` | GET | View friend's profile (friendship-gated) with shared relationship stats |
| `/friends/{relationship_id}` | DELETE | Unfriend — sets relationship status to `"ended"`, deletes pending requests |

> **Key Design Decision:** All friend requests start as `pending` regardless of profile visibility. The auto-accept logic for public profiles was intentionally removed to prevent users from appearing in the "Your Bonds" list without explicit consent.

