| `users` | id, email, name, gender, streak_days, last_login_date, total_xp | User profiles |
| `user_bots` | user_id, bot_id, xp, level, traits, language | User↔Bot relationship config |
| `messages` | user_id, bot_id, role, content, created_at | Chat message history |
| `memories` | user_id, bot_id, memory, category, rfm_magnitude, embedding | Long-term memory store |
