## 18. Known Issues & Blockers

| Issue | Severity | Module | Description |
|-------|----------|--------|-------------|
| Memory Worker Verification | Medium | `workers/` | The `workers/` directory is empty — RabbitMQ consumer logic runs inline in `background_tasks.py` but needs extraction for horizontal scaling |
| Legacy XP Parity | Low | `voice_ultra.py` | Lines 117-127 attempt to import from non-existent `reference_main` and `MM2.user_xp` — always falls through to fallback |
| Selfie Feature Toggle | Low | `selfie.py` | Composite selfie (user+bot) code is fully commented out; depends on user avatar availability |
| Image Meme Generation | Low | `multimodal.py` | Image-based meme generation commented out (budget constraint); only text memes active |
| Diary CRON Stub | Low | `diary.py` | `POST /api/diary/cron/daily` endpoint is a stub returning `{"success": True}` |
| Table Name Typo | Info | `database.txt` | Messages table is `messages_realtime_comunicatio_realtime` (typo in "comunicatio") — preserved for backwards compatibility |

